UML:TaggedValue.value: The agile project management view is created if you wish to use EA to strategically view the contents of what is in a kanban board. This is set up to link teams, the org and the projects in motion.
The Feature T-Shirt Size Breakdown provides a breakdown of the backlog and the total size of the features.
These template diagrams are meant to be copied for use in the main model. Using these templates allows trace ability and DSM analysis on roadmap quarters, years etc.
